# üß† AI Component Generator for React

**AI Component Generator** is a developer tool that lets you automatically generate components(UI + logic) for a website using AI. It provides a live **Preview** of the component and a **Code** view side-by-side. You can copy the code or download it as a file for direct integration into your projects.

