## ‚ú® Features

- **AI-powered generation** of complete website component files (JSX + CSS / styling).  
- **Live preview** of the component as you generate or fine-tune it.  
- **Code view** shows the exact source code for the rendered component.  
- **Copy to clipboard** or **Download as file (.jsx / .js / .tsx)**.  
- Supports commonly used libraries: props, state, context, hooks, styling (CSS / styled-components) etc.  
- Extensible ‚Äî you can plug in more templates or override the generation logic.  
- Clean and modern UI: split pane for preview + code, dark/light theme support.

---


## üèÅ Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js (version 14+ recommended)  
- npm or yarn  
- (Optional) An API key or configuration for your AI backend (if using a hosted model or service)  

### Installation

1. Clone this repository:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/react-ai-component-generator.git
   cd react-ai-component-generator
